//////// Processus

@proc_def ::pitch_seq_in($track, $in, $durs, $pitch, $dev, $tempo, $track_bus, $amp = 0)
{
	@local $durtab, $fact_dur := 1, $pitch_seq_amp := 0

	$durtab := @choose($durs)

	loop $durtab @label pitch_seq @tempo $tempo ;$tempo1 ;@tempo 20 
	{
		$tracks($track).group_add([[AudioInput, input, $in, amp, $amp], [TMFxPitch2, pitch, @choose($pitch)+@rand($dev)], [OutEnv1_HOA7, env, @choose($envs(server1).domain()), dur, $durtab*$fact_dur, coords, [@rand_range(0.5, 2), @rand_range(-180, 180), 0], amp, 0, globTBus, $track_bus]])		
		$durtab := @choose($durs)
	}
}

whenever ($refresh_samp == $refresh_samp) // refresh samples from Max to servers
{
	::refresh_samples("server2")
	::refresh_samples("server3")
	::refresh_samples("server4")
}

whenever ($refresh_vezer2nim == $refresh_vezer2nim) // refresh vezer2nim from Max
{
	::refresh_vezer2nim()
}


whenever ($notify_5 == $notify_5)
{
	$Servers("server5").notify(1)
}

NOTE 60 1 waveshaping_buffs

// create a waveshaping buffer
$tab_sin := [ @sin(@scale($x, 0, 1025, (-1*$pi/2), ($pi/2), 1)) | $x in (1025) ] // create tab	
$tab_sin_2 := []
forall $x in $tab_sin
{
	@local $x_new
	$x_new := (@cos(@scale($x, -1, 1, 0, $pi*50, 1)*0.08) / 4) + 0.3
	$tab_sin_2.push_back($x*$x_new)
}
$tab_sin_2 := @normalize($tab_sin_2, -1, 1) // normalize signal between -1 and 1

// print (""+$tab_sin_2)
// send result to sc server buffer
::asWavetableNoWrapTab("server3", "wt_shaper1", $tab_sin_2) // "wt_shaper1" name in dictionary to store the buffer ID

$add_level := -30

			// obj::granos_addict("mes_78_4_1", "group_hoa1", [0.5, 8, 4], [-75, -3, -10, -75], [0.5, 1], [2, 90, 0], [1, 90, 90], dir = 1, envbuf0 = "pointe", envbuf1 = "inv", prob = 0.9, tmp = 120, chg_tmp = [60, 120, 200, 60], chg_ifac = [0, 0.25, 0.5, 1], chg_grain_dur = [0.03, 0.05, 0.05, 0.03])

@obj_def granos_addict($nota_name, $mix_group, $dur = [0.5, 8, 4], $amps = [-75, -3, -10, -75], $pitch_gliss = [0.5, 1], $coords_start = [2, 90, 0], $coords_end = [1, 90, 90], $dir = 1, $envbuf0 = "pointe", $envbuf1 = "inv", $trig_rate = [1, 20, 30, 1], $chg_ifac = [0, 0.25, 0.5, 1], $chg_grain_dur = [0.03, 0.05, 0.05, 0.03], $preset = "synth6_2")
{
	@local $len, $synth_server
    @init 
    {

		$len := $dur.sum()
		$synth_server := $SC_Groups($mix_group)("server_name")

		obj::crea_track_HOA($nota_name, $mix_group, fade_in = 1, amp = -120, in_channels = 1, [["TAddic_5_8", "preset", $preset, "lag", 0], ["TGranInterp", "trigRate", 1, "dur", 0.0020000000949949, "durDev", 0.0, "ifac", 0.0, "ampDev", 0.0, "envbuf0", ($envs($synth_server)($envbuf0)), "envbuf1", ($envs($synth_server)($envbuf1))]])

		print granos_addict_synth_server $synth_server
		// $tracks($nota_name).set("TGranInterp", ["dur", 0.0050000000949949, "durDev", 0.0, "ifac", 0.0, "ampDev", 0.0])
		// $tracks($nota_name).set("TGranInterp", ["envbuf0", ($envs("server1")("rond")), "envbuf1", ($envs("server1")("perc"))])

		$tracks($nota_name).bpf_param("TGranInterp", "trigRate", [$trig_rate[0], $dur[0], "circ", $trig_rate[1], $dur[1], $trig_rate[2]  , $dur[2], $trig_rate[3]])

		$tracks($nota_name).bpf_param("TAddic_5_8", "transp", [$pitch_gliss[0], $len, "quart_out", $pitch_gliss[1]])
		$tracks($nota_name).bpf_param("TGranInterp", "dur", [$chg_grain_dur[0], $dur[0], "circ", $chg_grain_dur[1], $dur[1], $chg_grain_dur[2]  , $dur[2], $chg_grain_dur[3]]) 
		$tracks($nota_name).bpf_param("TGranInterp", "ifac", [$chg_ifac[0], $dur[0], "circ", $chg_ifac[1], $dur[1], $chg_ifac[2]  , $dur[2], $chg_ifac[3]]) 
		$tracks($nota_name).amp(				  [$amps[0],    $dur[0], "circ", $amps[1]    , $dur[1], $amps[2]      , $dur[2], $amps[3]])
		// $tracks($nota_name).change_proc_tempo([$chg_tmp[0], $dur[0], "circ", $chg_tmp[1], $dur[1], $chg_tmp[2]  , $dur[2], $chg_tmp[3]])
		// $tracks($nota_name).source_cart_traj_bpf(0.5, [-1, 5, "circ", 0, 12, 1], [0.5, 5, "circ", 1, 12, 2])
		// $tracks($nota_name).source_cart_traj_bpf([$x_in, $dur_a, "circ", 0, $dur[2], $x_out], [$y_in, $dur_a, "circ", 0, $dur[2], $y_out], [$z_in, $dur_a, "circ", 0, $dur[2], $z_out])

		$tracks($nota_name).traj_circ_interp2($coords_start, $coords_end, $len, $dir) 	
		($len+0.01) $tracks($nota_name).free(0.1)
	}
}

@proc_def grain_notes_db12($pitch, $dur, $sample, $env, $x, $y, $z, $amp) 
{
	::HOAmbi_grain_xyz_track_buf([$SF_map("server6")($sample+".aif")], $env, @transratio($pitch-6000), @dur2sec($dur), 0.0, [$x, $y, $z], $amp, "notas_elec") 
}

@proc_def grain_notes_HOA($pitch, $dur, $sample, $env, $x, $y, $z, $amp) 
{
	::HOAmbi_grain_xyz_track_buf([$SF_map("server6")($sample+".aif")], $env, @transratio($pitch-6000), @dur2sec($dur), 0.0, [$x, $y, $z], $amp, "notas_elec_HOA") 
}

@proc_def samples($pitch, $dur, $sample, $env, $x1, $y1, $z1, $x2, $y2, $z2, $amp) 
{
	// $tracks("notas_elec_ste").play_sample_ste_HOA($sample, $amp, [$x1, $y1, $z1, $x2, $y2, $z2])
	$tracks("notas_elec").play_sample_ste_HOA($sample, $amp, [$x1, $y1, $z1, $x2, $y2, $z2])
}

@proc_def samples_HOA($pitch, $dur, $sample, $env, $x1, $y1, $z1, $x2, $y2, $z2, $amp) 
{
	// $tracks("notas_elec_ste").play_sample_ste_HOA($sample, $amp, [$x1, $y1, $z1, $x2, $y2, $z2])
	$tracks("notas_elec_HOA").play_sample_ste_HOA($sample, $amp, [$x1, $y1, $z1, $x2, $y2, $z2])
}

@proc_def samples2($pitch, $dur, $sample, $env, $x1, $y1, $z1, $x2, $y2, $z2, $amp) 
{
	group
	{	
		@local $sf_name
		$sf_name := $sample
		// print sf_name ($sample)
		// print time ($dur/1000)
		$tracks("notas_elec").play_sample_ste_HOA($sample, $amp, [$x1, $y1, $z1, $x2, $y2, $z2])
		$dur $tracks("notas_elec").play_sampleHOA_stop($sf_name) // ($dur/1000)s
	}
}

// ::sr_synth(4 , wavetable1 , 1)
@proc_def sr_synth($dur, $wavetable, $amp, $rel = 0.1)
{
	switch ($wavetable)
	{
		case "wavetable1":
		$rand_note := [1600, 8525., 3525., 4050., 2900., 7400., 7125., 8875., 4600., 4300.] // $rand_note := [1600,2900]
		$rand_amp := [-24, -30, -22, -30, -23, -28, -21, -29, -29, -27]
		case "wavetable2":
		$rand_note := [1600, 9675., 4100., 8350., 7525., 5550., 5850., 9625., 9025., 7050.]
		$rand_amp := [-21, -25, -21, -21, -27, -29, -26, -21, -25, -24]
		case "wavetable3":
		$rand_note := [1600, 6400., 7375., 8500., 3225., 7500., 4025., 4700., 4950., 8575.]
		$rand_amp := [-21, -25, -21, -21, -27, -29, -26, -21, -25, -24]
		case "wavetable4":
		$rand_note := [1600, 6875., 6275., 6825., 7000., 6975., 7175., 6925., 7150., 7050., 7100., 6550.]
		$rand_amp := [-25, -22, -19, -17, -19, -19, -19, -25, -25, -18, -24, -17]
		case "wavetable5":
		$rand_note := [1600, 6900., 6725., 6050., 6325., 7075., 7100., 6075., 6375., 6900., 6950., 6675.]
		$rand_amp := [-24, -22, -18, -17, -16, -18, -16, -18, -24, -16, -19, -20]
		case "wavetable6":
		$rand_note := [1600, 7425., 6700., 6475., 7050., 7300., 6025., 7050., 7000., 7175., 6925., 6675.]
		$rand_amp := [-19, -22, -25, -16, -23, -19, -21, -17, -18, -16, -17, -20]
		case "wavetable7":
		$rand_note := [1600, 7275., 7100., 7325., 6300., 6475., 6475., 6800., 6425., 6075., 6575., 7050.]
		$rand_amp := [-23, -22, -16, -17, -16, -19, -17, -21, -23, -21, -21, -23]
		case "wavetable8":
		$rand_note := [1600, 6375., 7200., 7450., 6700., 6150., 7050., 6375., 6725., 7025., 6500., 7250.]
		$rand_amp := [-18, -24, -21, -18, -24, -22, -22, -25, -18, -19, -20, -17]
		case "wavetable9":
		$rand_note := [1600, 6300., 6650., 7350., 6275., 6250., 7325., 7325., 6425., 6825., 7400., 6525.]
		$rand_amp := [-23, -25, -16, -24, -18, -24, -25, -21, -19, -20, -16, -22]
		case "wavetable10":
		$rand_note := [1600., 4775., 4825., 4950., 5225., 5425., 6050., 6225., 7400., 7875., 9150., 9600.]
		$rand_amp := [-23, -25, -16, -24, -18, -24, -25, -21, -19, -20, -16, -22]
	}
	forall $note in $rand_note.size()
	{
		$tracks("track_waveshaping").mod_add(["Shaper2_HOAambi7", "buf", $WavetableNoWrapTab("wt_shaper1"), "freq", $rand_note[$note].midic2hz(), "amp", $rand_amp[$note]+$amp, "atk", 0.01, "sus", @dur2sec($dur), "rel", $rel, "curvemax", 0, "globTBus", $tracks("track_waveshaping").$bus, "coords", [1, (360/$rand_note.size()*$note)-180, 0]], fade_in = 0.001)
	}	
}

$map_granulations := map{}

@proc_def sr_proc1($proc, $dur, $amp = 0)
{
	switch ($proc)
	{
		case "gran_cor_trp1":
			group 
			{
				// @local $gran_proc
				// $gran_proc := obj::HOAmbi_grain_xyz_rand_fix_track_buf_list([$SF_map("server3")("trb-la3+.aif"), $SF_map("server3")("trp-fa5.aif")], "carre", 1, 1, 0, 0, 0.07, 0.07, 0.1, 0.1, -1, 1, -1, 1, 0, 0.6, $amp, "gran_proc", 1)
				if($map_granulations("gran_cor_trp1").is_undef())
				{

					$dur $map_granulations("gran_cor_trp1").free(10)
					5.1 $map_granulations.remove("gran_cor_trp1")
				}

			}
		case "gliss1": // dur 8 amp 6
		{
			group @tempo $RT_TEMPO
			{
				obj::crea_track_HOA("add_gliss1", "group_hoa3", fade_in = 0.1, amp = $amp, in_channels = 1,[TAddic_20_8, transp, 2.607, amp, -25, d, 4.3000001907349, shift, 0.0, distor, 0.0, lfnoise_amp, 0.0010000000474975, lag, 0.0010000000474975, width, 2.0, lag_spat, 0.20000000298023, freqs, [ 808.28002929688, 870.34002685547, 870.34002685547, 1009.1400146484, 1297.7600097656, 1460.8499755859, 1460.8499755859, 1573.0200195312, 1573.0200195312, 1693.8100585938, 1693.8100585938, 1693.8100585938, 2451.9899902344, 2451.9899902344, 2451.9899902344, 3061.330078125, 3822.1000976562, 4115.6000976562, 3701.5100097656, 6765.3798828125 ], amps, [ 0.40000000596046, 1.1599999666214, 0.75999999046326, 1.2699999809265, 1.3899999856949, 0.87999999523163, 1.0499999523163, 1.8799999952316, 1.0099999904633, 0.37000000476837, 1.4700000286102, 0.54000002145767, 1.0499999523163, 1.5499999523163, 1.0800000429153, 0.28999999165535, 1.9700000286102, 0.25999999046326, 1.5299999713898, 1.8600000143051 ], pos, [ 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05 ]]) // track for receive encoded HOA (granulation, etc)
				$tracks("add_gliss1").bpf_param(TAddic_20_8, transp, [2.607, $dur, "circ_in", 0.165])
				$dur $tracks("add_gliss1").free(0.1)
			}
		}
		case "gliss2": // dur 4 amp 6
		{
			group 
			{
				obj::crea_track_HOA("add_gliss2", "group_hoa3", fade_in = 0.1, amp = $amp, [TAddic_20_8, transp, 2.607, amp, -25, d, 10, shift, -0.1, distor, 0.2, lfnoise_amp, 0.0010000000474975, lag, 0.0010000000474975, width, 2.0, lag_spat, 0.20000000298023, freqs, [ 808.28002929688, 870.34002685547, 870.34002685547, 1009.1400146484, 1297.7600097656, 1460.8499755859, 1460.8499755859, 1573.0200195312, 1573.0200195312, 1693.8100585938, 1693.8100585938, 1693.8100585938, 2451.9899902344, 2451.9899902344, 2451.9899902344, 3061.330078125, 3822.1000976562, 4115.6000976562, 3701.5100097656, 6765.3798828125 ], amps, [ 0.40000000596046, 1.1599999666214, 0.75999999046326, 1.2699999809265, 1.3899999856949, 0.87999999523163, 1.0499999523163, 1.8799999952316, 1.0099999904633, 0.37000000476837, 1.4700000286102, 0.54000002145767, 1.0499999523163, 1.5499999523163, 1.0800000429153, 0.28999999165535, 1.9700000286102, 0.25999999046326, 1.5299999713898, 1.8600000143051 ], pos, [ 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05, 9.9999997473788e-05 ]]) // track for receive encoded HOA (granulation, etc)

					curve
			      	@Grain := 5 ms //0.01s 
			      	@action :=  { 
					// $map_granulations("gran_cor2_fa3").rate_min($val1)
					// $map_granulations("gran_cor2_fa3").rate_max($val1)
					$map_granulations("gran_cor2_fa3").env_dur_min($val1)
					$map_granulations("gran_cor2_fa3").env_dur_max($val1)
		        }
		        { $val1 {
		                 	{0.2 	} @type := "circ_in"
		                 3 	{0.06 } 
		               	}
		        }
					$dur $map_granulations("gran_cor2_fa3").free(3)
					$map_granulations.remove("gran_cor2_fa3")
				}
			}	
		case "gran_trb1": // 16, 10
			group @tempo $RT_TEMPO
			{
				// @local $notas_elec_HOA
				// $notas_elec_HOA := obj::HOAmbi_grain_xyz_rand_fix_track_buf_list([$SF_map("server3")("trb-la3+.aif"), $SF_map("server3")("trp-fa5.aif")], "carre", 1, 1, 0, 0, 0.07, 0.07, 0.1, 0.1, -1, 1, -1, 1, 0, 0.6, $amp, "notas_elec_HOA", 1)
				if($map_granulations("gran_trb1").is_undef())
				{
					$map_granulations.add_pair("gran_trb1", obj::HOAmbi_grain_xyz_rand_fix_track_buf_list([$SF_map("server6")("trb-sol2.aif")], "carre", 0.99, 1.01, 0.3, 0.8, 0.08, 0.1, 0.1, 0.1, $trb_cart[0],$trb_cart[0], $trb_cart[1],$trb_cart[1], 0., 1, $amp, "gran_proc", 2))
					$map_granulations("gran_trb1").xyz_interpol([[$trb_cart[0],$trb_cart[0], $trb_cart[1],$trb_cart[1], 0., 1], 10, "linear", [$trp_cart[0],$trp_cart[0], $trp_cart[1],$trp_cart[1], 0., 1]], 1)
					$dur $map_granulations("gran_trb1").free(3)
					$map_granulations.remove("gran_trb1")
				}
			}								

	}
}

@proc_def sr_proc2($proc, $amp = 0)
{
	switch ($proc)
	{		
		case "wavetable_amp9_desc":
		$tracks("track_waveshaping").amp([-10, 6, -15]) //-10 base
		case "wavetable_amp9_asc":
		$tracks("track_waveshaping").amp([-15, 10, -7]) //-10 base						
		case "gran_cor_trp1_gliss":
		{
			group @tempo $RT_TEMPO
			{
				@local $val1, $val2, $amp1
				curve
		      	@Grain := 10 ms //0.01s 
		      	@action :=  { 
		        // $gran_proc.rate_min($val)
				// $gran_proc.rate_max($val)
				$map_granulations("gran_cor_trp1").rate_min($val1)
				$map_granulations("gran_cor_trp1").rate_max($val1)
				$map_granulations("gran_cor_trp1").pos_min($val2)
				$map_granulations("gran_cor_trp1").pos_max($val2)
		        }
		        { $val1, $val2	{
		                 	{1,		0  } @type := "circ_in"
		                 8 	{0.23,	0.5} 
		               	}
		        }	
				curve
		      	@Grain := 10 ms //0.01s 
		      	@action :=  { 
				$map_granulations("gran_cor_trp1").amp($amp1)
		        }
		        { $amp1	{
		                 	{-6} @type := "linear"
		                 8 	{0} 
		               	}
		        }					        

			}

		}
		// case "gran_trb1":
		// 	group @tempo $RT_TEMPO
		// 	{
		// 		// @local $gran_proc
		// 		// $gran_proc := obj::HOAmbi_grain_xyz_rand_fix_track_buf_list([$SF_map("server3")("trb-la3+.aif"), $SF_map("server3")("trp-fa5.aif")], "carre", 1, 1, 0, 0, 0.07, 0.07, 0.1, 0.1, -1, 1, -1, 1, 0, 0.6, $amp, "gran_proc", 1)

@proc_def ::sr_fx($proc)
{
	switch ($proc)
	{
		case "fx_cordes_mes156":
			group 
			{
				obj::crea_track_HOA("specCombN_m60_vln", "group_hoa3", fade_in = 1, amp = 0, doppler = 0, in_channels = 1, control_name = fx, [["AudioInput", "input", $vln, "amp", 0], ["STM_specCombN", "preset", "sax-sec3"]])
				$tracks("specCombN_m60_vln").dae($vln_dae)
				obj::crea_track_HOA("fsht_vln", "group_hoa1", fade_in = 4, amp = 0, doppler = 0, in_channels = 1, control_name = fx, [["AudioInput", "input", $vln, "amp", 0], ["TMFxShift2"], ["TJPverb_mono", t60, 2]])
				$tracks("fsht_vln").rand_lfo("TMFxShift2", "modfreq", -40, 40, 0, "exp", 60)
				$tracks("fsht_vln").dae($vln_dae)

whenever samp_instr ($samp_instr==$samp_instr)
{
	// print $samp_instr
	// 	@fun_def play_sampleHOA($sample, $ampli = 0, $coord = [1, 0, 0], $loop = 0) // only track no_encoder
	switch ($samp_instr[0])
	{
		case "flute-samp":
		group
		{
			$tracks("flute-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $fl_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("flute-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "hautbois-samp":
		group
		{	
			print samp_instr (""+$samp_instr)
			$tracks("hautbois-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $htb_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("hautbois-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
			print stop 
		}

		case "clarinette-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("clarinette-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $cl_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("clarinette-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "basson-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("basson-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $bsn_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("basson-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "cor1-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("cor1-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $cor1_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("cor1-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "cor2-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("cor2-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $cor2_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("cor2-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "trompette-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("trompette-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $trp_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("trompette-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "trombone-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("trombone-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $trb_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("trombone-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "violon-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("violon-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $vln_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("violon-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "alto-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("alto-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $alto_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("alto-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "violoncelle-samp":
		group
		{		
			$tracks("violoncelle-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $vlc_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("violoncelle-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}

		case "contrebasse-samp":
		group
		{	
		// print samp_instr ($samp_instr[1])
		// print samp_amp (@a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6])
		// print (""+$SF_map("server6")($samp_instr[1]))
			$tracks("contrebasse-samp").play_sampleHOA($samp_instr[1], @a2dB($samp_instr[4]/127)+$samp_instr[6], $cb_dae)
			($samp_instr[5])ms $tracks("contrebasse-samp").play_sampleHOA_stop($samp_instr[1])
		}
	}
}

		$tracks("warp1_play_cb_mes_45").traj_circ_interp($cb_dae, $bsn_dae, 8.2) 

		$rec_buf7_2.rec($trp)

		obj::crea_track_HOA("warp1_play_trp_mes_45", "group_hoa1", fade_in = 1, amp = 0, doppler = 0, in_channels = 1, control_name = warping, [["Warp1Play", buf, $rec_buf7_2.id(), envbuf, $envs("server1")("perc")], ["TJPverb_mono", t60, 2]]) // track without encoder 
		$tracks("warp1_play_trp_mes_45").rand_lfo_dyn("Warp1Play", "pos", 0.0, "linear", 60, $rec_buf7_2)
		$tracks("warp1_play_trp_mes_45").traj_circ_interp($cb_dae, $bsn_dae, 8.2) 

		group mes_mes_46
		{
			// $rec_buf7_2.rec($trp)
			group 
			{
				$amp_mes_mes_46 := -3
				$dur_mes_46 := 7
				$amp_end_mes_46 := 0
				$dur_gliss_mes_46 := 3
				@local $loop_dur := @rand_range(0.1, 0.5), $local_loop

				obj::crea_track_HOA("cortaRand_mesmes_46", "group_hoa1", fade_in = 0.1, amp = $amp_mes_mes_46, doppler = 0, in_channels = 1, control_name = randbuf, [["TCortaRandBuf", "buf", $rec_buf7_2.id(), "loopDur", 0.1]]) //, [CompressorD, thresh, 0.02, slopeBelow, 0.2, slopeAbove, 1, clampTime,  0.0019, relaxTime, 0.0028]])  //, [Norm, lev, 0.03]
				$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_46").amp([$amp_mes_mes_46, 1, $amp_mes_mes_46, $dur_gliss_mes_46-1, "quad", $amp_end_mes_46, $dur_mes_46, $amp_end_mes_46, 3, -10, 4, -60], free = 0.1) //, action = ["clearbuf", $rec_buf7_2])
				// $tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_46").traj_circ_interp($fl_dae, $bsn_dae, $dur_gliss_mes_46) 
				$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_46").dae_rand_lfo([0.8, 2, $trp_dae[0], -180, 180, $trp_dae[1], 0, 20, $trp_dae[2]], 20)
				$local_loop := {
					loop $loop_dur
					{
						$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_46").set(TCortaRandBuf, [trig_time, @rand_range(2, 5)])
						$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_46").set(TCortaRandBuf, [loopDur, $loop_dur])
						$loop_dur := @rand_range(0.1, 0.5)
					}
					(1+$dur_gliss_mes_46-1+$dur_mes_46+3+4) abort $local_loop
				}

			}

			// $tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_46").amp(3)
		}
	}
}

group mes_78 @tempo := $RT_TEMPO
{
	group 
	{
		group vents_78_n2

			1.5 whenever htb_ampgate_mes78_n2 (($ampgatedetect[0] == "server5") && ($ampgatedetect[1] == $htb))
			{
				group mes_78_n2
				{
					$rec_buf4_1.rec($htb)
					$amp_htb_mes_78_n2 := 0
					$dur_htb_mes_78_n2 := 6
					$amp_end_mes_78_n2 := 1
					$dur_gliss_mes_78_n2 := 3
					@local $loop_dur := @rand_range(0.1, 0.5), $local_loop

					obj::crea_track_HOA("cortaRand_mesmes_78_n2", "group_hoa1", fade_in = 0.1, amp = $amp_htb_mes_78_n2, doppler = 0, in_channels = 1, control_name = randbuf, [["TCortaRandBuf", "buf", $rec_buf4_1.id(), "loopDur", 0.1]]) //, [CompressorD, thresh, 0.02, slopeBelow, 0.2, slopeAbove, 1, clampTime,  0.0019, relaxTime, 0.0028]])  //, [Norm, lev, 0.03]
					$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_78_n2").amp([$amp_htb_mes_78_n2, $dur_htb_mes_78_n2, $amp_end_mes_78_n2, 1 , -60], free = 0.1) //, action = ["clearbuf", $rec_buf4_1])
					// $tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_78_n2").traj_circ_interp($fl_dae, $bsn_dae, $dur_gliss_mes_78_n2) 
					$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_78_n2").dae_rand_lfo([0.8, 2, $htb_dae[0], -180, 180, $htb_dae[1], 0, 90, $htb_dae[2]], 10)
					$local_loop := {
						loop $loop_dur
						{
							$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_78_n2").set(TCortaRandBuf, [trig_time, @rand_range(2, 5)])
							$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_78_n2").set(TCortaRandBuf, [loopDur, $loop_dur])
							$loop_dur := @rand_range(0.1, 0.5)
						}
					}
					($dur_htb_mes_78_n2) abort $local_loop
				}
				abort htb_ampgate_mes78_n2 @norec // abort juste après le onset
			}
		}

				$tracks("chop_trp_78_n2").set("TCortaRandBuf", ["fadeTime", 0.0015]) // trigger chop

			whenever vlc_ampgate_mes73 (($ampgatedetect[0] == "server5") && ($ampgatedetect[1] == $vlc))

					$local_loop := {
						loop $loop_dur
						{
							$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_73_vlc").set(TCortaRandBuf, [trig_time, @rand_range(2, 5)])
							$tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_73_vlc").set(TCortaRandBuf, [loopDur, $loop_dur])
							$loop_dur := @rand_range(0.1, 0.2)
						}
					}

					($dur_mes_73_vlc) abort $local_loop
					// $tracks("cortaRand_mesmes_73_vlc").amp(3)
				}

	group voice_electronique2_mes_304 // 305-306-307-308-309-310-311-312-313+314-315-316-317
	{
		@local $loc_azi, $loc_ele
		curve
	  	@Grain := 10 ms //0.01s 
	  	@action :=  {
	  		if($loc_azi > 180)
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi - 360
			}
			else
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			}
			if($loc_azi < -180)
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			}	
			else
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			}							
	  	}
	    { $loc_azi	{
	             	 {0}
	             0.5 {0}
	             4.5 {270}  @type := "linear"
	             6 	 {270} 
	             4.5   {-30} 
	           	}
	    }
		curve
	  	@Grain := 10 ms //0.01s

		     	 {0}
		     0.5 {0}

		   	}

group @tempo $RT_TEMPO
{	
	group voice_samples_mes_320
	{
		@local $local_dist, $loc_azi1, $loc_azi2
		curve
	  	@Grain := 10 ms //0.01s 
	  	@action :=  {
	  		// if($loc_azi > 180)
			// {
			// 	$loc_azi := $loc_azi - 360
			// }
			// else
			// {
			// 	$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			// }
			// if($loc_azi < -180)
			// {
			// 	$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			// }	
			// else
			// {
			// 	$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			// }							
	  	}
	    { $local_dist, $loc_azi1, $loc_azi2	{
	             	 {-3, 0, 0} @type := "linear"
	             5 {3, 180, -180} 
	             
	           	}
	    }	
		// 0 silence 1 
		3/4 ::samples( 7100.000 , 1 , 23_hourglass.aif , perc_sust , $local_dist , $loc_azi1 , 0 , $local_dist , $loc_azi2 , 0 , -11 )

NOTE 60 4 mes_362

print mes_362

group @tempo $RT_TEMPO
{
	group voice_electronique_mes_363 
	{
		@local $loc_azi
		curve
	  	@Grain := 10 ms //0.01s 
	  	@action :=  {
	  		if($loc_azi > 180)
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi - 360
			}
			else
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			}
			if($loc_azi < -180)
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			}	
			else
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			}							
	  	}
	    { $loc_azi	{
	             	 {30} @type := "linear"
	             2.5 {270} 
	             3   {-30} 
	           	}
	    }	
	    //   grain_notes_db12($pitch, $dur, $sample, $env, $x, $y, $z, $amp) 

			::grain_notes_db12(8100.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(8000.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(7912.598, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(7832.197, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(7733.444, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(7618.330, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(7488.240, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(7344.212, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(7187.066, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(7017.474, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6835.997, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6643.117, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 1, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, $loc_azi, -7, -6)

		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, -$loc_azi, -7, -6)
		1/8 ::grain_notes_db12(6650.000, 1/8, trb-do#4-bisb_freeze_mono, carre2b, 0, -$loc_azi, -7, -6)

		@local $loc_azi, $loc_ele

			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi - 360
			}

	group voice_electronique2_mes_378
	{
		@local $loc_azi, $loc_ele
		curve
	  	@Grain := 10 ms //0.01s 
	  	@action :=  {
	  		if($loc_azi > 180)
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi - 360
			}
			else
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi
			}
			if($loc_azi < -180)
			{
				$loc_azi := $loc_azi + 360
			}	
	  	}
	    { $loc_azi	{
	             	{180} @type := "linear" //coord trp
	             2 	{-180} 
	           	}
	    }	
		curve
	  	@Grain := 10 ms //0.01s 
	    { $loc_ele	{
	             	 {-20} @type := "linear" //coord trp
	             0.5 {40} 
	             0.5 {-20} 
	             0.5 {50} 
	             0.5 {-10}   
	           	}
	    }			
		// 0 silence 1
		1 silence 1
